headline: Brown & Brown (BRO) Declares US$0.15 Dividend Payable August 2025
summary: Brown & Brown (BRO) recently affirmed a quarterly cash dividend of $0.15 per share, payable on August 20, 2025. Over the last week, the company's stock price moved slightly by 1.71%, while the broader market rose by 1.7%. This dividend declaration signifies the company's ongoing commitment to shareholder value, but the market dynamics suggest the effect on the share price was minimal, contributing to broader market trends instead.
